    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been consistently maintained. The exterior paint still holds a nice luster, though upon close inspection, you will notice some minor stone chips on the front bumper and a few light scratches from everyday use. The interior is clean and smoke-free, showing only moderate wear on the driver's side seat and some slight fading on the most-used buttons. Mechanically, the car performs well, shifts smoothly, and has no dashboard warning lights. It is a dependable choice for anyone looking for a well-kept vehicle that is ready for the road.",
